The '''Justice Council''' was the council of the [[New Republic Senate/Legends|Senate]] charged with judicial matters in the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]]. The Justice Council was also tasked with approving nominees to the [[Court of Justice]] made by the [[Chief of State (New Republic)/Legends|Chief of State]]. Internally, it also ruled on legal charges made against members of the Senate. The Chair of the Justice Council was a member of the [[New Republic Ruling Council|Ruling Council]], and was also the [[Minister of Justice (New Republic)|Minister of Justice]].

[[Borsk Fey'lya]] served as Chair of the Justice Council during the [[Yevethan Purge]] and [[Caamas Document Crisis]]. After Fey'lya was elected Chief of State, [[Ta'laam Ranth]] became Chair of the Justice Council.

